title: Two Sides to Every Date: You Said You Were Into It!
description: Kelly is wondering what happened with Brandon.  They had gone out to dinner and hung out at her place for a little while after and when the date ended she said "let's do this again" and he agreed but since then he's fallen off and barely texted her back.  We talk to Kelly AND Brandon to find out what happened!
